WEBVTT

00:03:31.080 --> 00:03:34.400
One of the first things
Paul said to me after his diagnosis was,

00:03:35.360 --> 00:03:36.880
"I want you to get remarried."

00:03:38.480 --> 00:03:41.816
And I was like, whoa, I guess
we get to say anything out loud.

00:03:41.840 --> 00:03:44.376
(Laughter)

00:03:44.400 --> 00:03:46.456
It was so shocking

00:03:46.480 --> 00:03:48.280
and heartbreaking ...

00:03:49.440 --> 00:03:50.656
and generous,

00:03:50.680 --> 00:03:52.176
and really comforting

00:03:52.200 --> 00:03:54.776
because it was so starkly honest,

00:03:54.800 --> 00:03:57.920
and that honesty turned out
to be exactly what we needed.

00:03:58.760 --> 00:04:00.456
